com.ibm.team.repository.common.validation
Interface IStringSizeConstraintErrorStatus

All Superinterfaces:
IPropertyConstraintErrorStatus, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IStatus
public interface IStringSizeConstraintErrorStatus
extends IPropertyConstraintErrorStatus

Specialized status for string size constraint violations. Clients can cast to this to determine what the max size is and what the actual size is.

Since:
0.6
See Also:
IItemValidator, IPropertyConstraintErrorStatus, IPropertyConstraintErrorStatus.STRING_SIZE_CONSTRAINT
